PIRAs Latest Emissions Market Intelligence AnalysisPIRAs Emissions Marketing Intelligence Service EMIS just released its latest report to clients entitled Update The Southern California NOx RECLAIM Market On May the South Coast Air Quality Management District Board removed power generators as defined under the program from the NOx RECLAIM market at least until However their actions to date have left the rest of the RECLAIM participants such as oil refineries facing an ongoing extremely tight market balance A second extensive report analyzing trends and prospects in the SO Credit Market will be released shortly NonEMIS clients interested in the latest RECLAIM report can purchase it for The annual fee for quarterly EMIS reports is for up to users at one client site office For more information please contact Victoria Watkins at ext or
